   391→- [x] Persist `payment_saga_t` progress to EventStoreDB → replay after crash.  
   392→- [x] Encrypt payloads (`payload_encrypt()`) for PCI-DSS compliance.  
   393→- [x] Emit OpenTelemetry spans for distributed tracing.  
   394→- [ ] Add circuit-breakers around downstream services (coming Q3).  
   395→
