   394→## 4 ╱ 4 Lab exercises
   395→
   396→1. Extend `cg_tokenise_pan()` to call an FF3-1 library when `EDUPAY_FPE=1`.  
   397→   Verify that the output still passes Luhn and preserves BIN/IIN.
   398→
   399→2. Attach `cg_seal()` to the CQRS → Audit-Trail write model.  
   400→   Use Wireshark to confirm that events on the message bus no longer contain
   401→   clear-text PAN or student identifiers (FERPA §99.31).
   402→
   403→3. Fire up `valgrind --tool=memcheck ./demo` and inspect the heap after
   404→   `cg_secure_bzero()` executes. No clear-text secrets should appear.
