     2→ *  EduPay Ledger Academy
     3→ *  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
     4→ *  Disburse Stipend Saga Use-Case
     5→ *
     6→ *  File:    financial_aid_service/application/use_cases/disburse_stipend_saga.c
     7→ *  License: MIT
     8→ *
     9→ *  Description:
    10→ *      Implements the Saga-pattern orchestration that disburses student
    11→ *      stipends.  The saga coordinates the following participating services:
    12→ *
    13→ *          1. Compliance/KYC          – FERPA-aware identity & sanction checks
    14→ *          2. Payment Gateway         – Reserve + capture funds
    15→ *          3. Ledger Repository       – Immutable, event-sourced ledger entry
    16→ *          4. Stipend Repository      – Aggregate root for stipend domain
    17→ *          5. Event Bus               – Publishes domain & integration events
    18→ *          6. Audit Logger            – Immutable audit trail
    19→ *
    20→ *      Compensating transactions are issued on failure so that the system
    21→ *      remains eventually consistent across micro-services.
    22→ *
    23→ *  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
    24→ */
