## 5. Compliance and Consent

### 5.1 Regulatory Framework

Per `docs/architecture/05_security_and_compliance.md` and `docs/lessons/L03_Regulatory_Compliance_in_Code.md`, the auto-payment feature must comply with:

| Regulation | Requirement | Implementation |
|------------|-------------|----------------|
| **FERPA** | Student consent for financial data sharing | Explicit opt-in stored in student profile |
| **PCI-DSS** | Payment data security | Tokenization of any card data involved |
| **SOC 2** | Audit trail | Immutable event log of all consent changes and auto-payments |

### 5.2 Consent Storage

The student's auto-payment consent flag should be stored as a **first-class domain entity** in the Admissions bounded context:

**Location:** `src/services/admissions_service/domain/student_preferences.h`

```c
typedef struct {
    char     student_id[32];
    bool     auto_pay_tuition_enabled;
    time_t   consent_granted_at;
    time_t   consent_revoked_at;       /* 0 if currently consented */
    char     consent_version[16];      /* Terms version accepted */
    char     consent_channel[32];      /* How consent was obtained */
} student_payment_preferences_t;
```

### 5.3 Consent Check in Workflow

The consent check occurs at **Step 5** of the saga (before issuing `ApplyStipendToTuition`):

```c
/* In step_apply_to_tuition() */

/* Query the student balance projection for consent flag */
auto_payment_eligibility_t eligibility = {0};
int rc = query_auto_payment_eligibility(
    saga->request->student.student_id,
    &eligibility);

/* Explicit consent check - this is the compliance gate */
if (!eligibility.auto_pay_enabled) {
    saga_log_audit(saga, AUDIT_INFO,
                   "Student %s has not opted into auto-payment (consent required).",
                   saga->request->student.student_id);

    /* Per FERPA: Do not proceed without explicit consent */
    return true; /* Saga continues but skips auto-payment */
}
```

### 5.4 Audit Trail Requirements

Every auto-payment action must be logged to the immutable audit trail (per `docs/architecture/05_security_and_compliance.md:22-23`):

```c
/* Required audit entries */
audit_logger_log(audit, AUDIT_INFO, "AUTO_PAYMENT",
    "consent_verified", student_id, saga_id,
    "Student consent for auto-payment verified.");

audit_logger_log(audit, AUDIT_INFO, "AUTO_PAYMENT",
    "amount_calculated", student_id, saga_id,
    "Auto-payment amount: %ld cents (stipend: %ld, balance: %ld).",
    amount_to_apply, stipend_amount, outstanding_balance);

audit_logger_log(audit, AUDIT_INFO, "AUTO_PAYMENT",
    "applied_to_tuition", student_id, saga_id,
    "Stipend %s applied to tuition account %s.",
    stipend_id, tuition_account_id);
```

